<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-a: #07111f;
      --bg-b: #0c1f33;
      --panel: rgba(10, 16, 30, 0.78);
      --panel-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --text: #f8fafc;
      --muted: #9fb0c8;
      --accent: #7c3aed;
      --accent-2: #22c55e;
      --accent-3: #06b6d4;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Manrope", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.35), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 15%, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.25), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-a), var(--bg-b));
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before,
    body::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: auto;
      pointer-events: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(40px);
      opacity: 0.45;
    }

    body::before {
      width: 280px;
      height: 280px;
      left: -90px;
      bottom: -80px;
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.25);
    }

    body::after {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
      right: 40px;
      top: 90px;
      background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.2);
    }

    .page-shell {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      padding: 32px 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .hero-badge span {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--accent-2);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12);
    }

    .form-card {
      width: min(100%, 760px);
      border: 1px solid var(--panel-border);
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: var(--panel);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      padding: 30px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .form-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), transparent 35%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .form-head {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .form-head h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .form-head p {
      margin: 12px 0 0;
      max-width: 46ch;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .question-grid {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .question-block {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }

    .form-label {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #eef2ff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .form-select,
    .form-control {
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .form-select:focus,
    .form-control:focus {
      border-color: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.65);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.18);
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .form-select option {
      color: #0f172a;
    }

    .submit-row {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), #4f46e5 55%, var(--accent-3));
      border: none;
      border-radius: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.95rem 1.2rem;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 30px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.22);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 34px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.28);
    }

    .btn-primary:focus {
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.22);
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .form-card {
        padding: 22px;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      .question-block {
        padding: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <section class="form-card">
      <div class="form-head text-center text-sm-start">
        <div class="hero-badge"><span></span> Rychlá anonymní anketa</div>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p>Vyplň krátký formulář a po odeslání se odpovědi zobrazí v přehledu výsledků.</p>
      </div>

      <form action="/submit" method="POST" class="question-grid">
        <div class="question-block">
          <label class="form-label">Oblíbený den v týdnu</label>

          <select class="form-select" name="den" required>
            <option value="">Vyber...</option>
            <option value="Pondělí">Pondělí</option>
            <option value="Úterý">Úterý</option>
            <option value="Středa">Středa</option>
            <option value="Čtvrtek">Čtvrtek</option>
            <option value="Pátek">Pátek</option>
            <option value="Sobota">Sobota</option>
            <option value="Neděle">Neděle</option>
          </select>
        </div>


        <div class="question-block">
          <label class="form-label">Jak často sportuješ během týdne?</label>

          <select class="form-select" name="sport" required>
            <option value="">Vyber...</option>
            <option value="nikdy">Nikdy</option>
            <option value="1-2x">1–2x týdně</option>
            <option value="3-4x">3–4x týdně</option>
            <option value="5+x">5x a více týdně</option>
          </select>
        </div>


        <div class="question-block">
          <label class="form-label">Jak nejraději trávíš volný čas?</label>

          <select class="form-select" name="volnycas" required>
            <option value="">Vyber...</option>
            <option value="sport">Sportem</option>
            <option value="knihy">Čtením knih</option>
            <option value="pc">Na počítači</option>
            <option value="rodina">S rodinou nebo přáteli</option>
          </select>
        </div>


        <div class="question-block">
          <label class="form-label">Komentář:</label>

          <textarea class="form-control" name="komentar" rows="3" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="submit-row">
          <button class="btn btn-primary w-100">
          Odeslat odpověď
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>

    </section>
  </main>

</body>

</html>